name: Cyber Sea Creatures - Leviathan
description: Living on the planet Ryu ravaged by war, Leviathan chose to support the winning side. Used by the royal navy on the frontlines for the toughest sea battles due to their sheer size in being able to take down enemy vessels with ease. Tentacles have the ability to regenerate with nanite technology. Unique poisonous tentacles allow it to take down even the toughest organic foes.
